1. Taj *smrad* iz kanalizacije je nepodnošljiv. (That *stench* from the sewer is unbearable.)
2. Ne želim da živim sa tim *smradom* od cimeta. (I don't want to live with that *pungent odor* of cinnamon.)
3. Ona *smrdi* na duvan. (She *smells* like tobacco.)
4. Moram da se oslobodim ovog *smrada* iz cipela. (I need to get rid of this *foul smell* from my shoes.)
5. Ovo je najgori *smrad* koji sam ikada osetio. (This is the worst *stench* I've ever smelled.)
6. Ovde *smrdi* kao u đubretu. (It *stinks* here like in a garbage dump.)
7. Ta hrana *smrdi* na pokvareno meso. (That food *smells* like spoiled meat.)
8. *Smrad* koji dolazi iz te kuhinje je strašan. (The *stench* coming from that kitchen is awful.)
9. Zatvorite nos, ovde *smrdi* na kanalizaciju. (Hold your nose, it *smells* like sewage here.)
10. Niko neće da radi u tom *smradu* od preduzeća. (No one wants to work in that *stinky* company.)

Note: Please keep in mind that the word "smrad" has a negative connotation and may be considered offensive in some situations.